      "description": "This meticulously maintained Lexus RX 350 strikes the perfect balance between luxury and utility. The exterior shines in a deep Obsidian finish, showing only minor road peppering on the front bumper consistent with careful highway use. Inside, the Parchment leather interior remains supple and clean; while there is light creasing on the driver\u2019s side bolster, the cabin is strictly smoke-free and devoid of tears or stains. Every feature\u2014from the dual-zone climate control to the premium surround-sound system\u2014functions exactly as intended. Mechanically, this vehicle is exceptionally sound, having received consistent synthetic oil changes every 5,000 miles and a recent set of Michelin tires with significant tread remaining. The transmission shifts seamlessly, and the brakes provide firm, confident stopping power. It comes with a complete set of service records, two key fobs, and the original all-weather floor mats. This is a turn-key vehicle ready for its next owner to enjoy immediately.",
